overview: Srinivas Katam working as a Lead Internet Marketing Specialist in Seo Company in India. Handling many in-house as well as clients projects on different themes. He has worked on websites from various industries, including Web designing, finance, real estate and health, travel & hotel. My job profile is to promote the in-house and clients websites on major search engines through organic search engine optimization & paid search techniques and to maintain their high rankings for the competitive keywords on major search engines.
